draft.title: SMARTYPANTS Funny Duck Christmas Card - Have A Quacking Christmas Pun Humour Seasons Greetings Card For Men Women Him Her Friend - Novelty Animal Xmas Card Design With Envelope
draft.description:
Tired of the same old boring Christmas cards? Add a splash of fun to the festive season with the SMARTYPANTS 'Have a Quacking Christmas' card! This design is guaranteed to bring a smile to anyone's face featuring three adorable ducks dressed in their festive best – including a cosy Christmas jumper and a quirky candy cane outfit. It's the perfect way to send warm wishes with a side of brilliant British humour.

Crafted from premium quality card stock with a vibrant professional print this card not only looks great but feels substantial too. The inside is left completely blank giving you all the space you need to write a personal message. Whether for a friend family member or a colleague this hilarious and charming card is a wonderful way to say Merry Christmas.

bullets: Quacking Christmas Humour – Perfect for spreading festive cheer this holiday season with a hilarious pun and a charming trio of ducks in Christmas jumpers and elf costumes.
Premium Quality Card – Expertly printed on thick 350gsm card stock for a superior feel and finish this card includes a high-quality rustic brown kraft envelope for stylish sending.
Blank For Your Message – Features a blank interior allowing you to write your own personalised heartfelt or funny message making it suitable for friends family and colleagues.
Vibrant Lasting Colours – Our professional printing process ensures the bright red background and charming duck illustrations are sharp vivid and resistant to fading over time.
Gift Ready Greetings – Arrives ready to be written and sent making it an effortless choice for Christmas greetings Secret Santa gifts or as a fun addition to a main present.
